# PHP

**Min PHP 7.4.**

## Practices (Clean Code, design patterns)

- **Clean Code**: small methods, clear names, early returns, minimal duplication
- **Design patterns**: when clarify structure (repository, strategy, factory) — no over-abstraction
- Business logic separate from WP hooks/templates where practical — no strict layers required
- No god files: split classes/files by responsibility; one file ≠ unrelated features
